Suzano Raises Pulp Prices by $30 a Ton in April, Valor Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-04-08T12:20:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/suzano-raises-pulp-prices-by-30-a-ton-in-april-valor-says.html
Suzano Papel & Celulose SA raised
pulp prices for the first time this year, increasing them by $30
a metric ton,  Valor Economico  reported, citing an unidentified
pulp industry executive.  The new prices took effect April 1, the Sao Paulo-based
newspaper said today, without disclosing the values.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 